 and l_shipdate < date \'1996-01-01\' + interval \'3\' month
 group by l_suppkey
)

 s_name,
 s_address,

 total_revenue
from supplier, revenue0
where s_suppkey = supplier_no
 and total_revenue = (

 from

 )
order by s_suppkey;":str, "default_pipe":str, 117:int);
